ent-RMCArmorM4RLight-name = M4R pattern CMB light armor
ent-RMCArmorM4RLight-desc = A dark set of armor, which is a modification of the security variant of Aegis Battlefield Armaments M3 armor. Designed for riot control and protest suppression in mind. The side of it has a metallic insignia with 'CMB RIOT CONTROL' on it. The laws of the Earth stretch beyond the Sol.
