ent-RMCArmorM4RMarshallMedium-name = M4R pattern CMB Marshal armor
ent-RMCArmorM4RMarshallMedium-desc = A custom fit variation of the CMB Riot armor, intended to be worn the Marshals themselves, has a golden lining with rank insignia. Has additional layer of lightweigh protective materials.
